graph TB
    subgraph ExtProc["AI Gateway Payload Processing (BBR ExtProc Host)"]
        direction TB

        subgraph PluginPipeline["Plugin Pipeline (ordered)"]
            direction TB
            ModelExtractor["body-field-to-header<br/>(upstream plugin)<br/>Extracts model field → header"]
            ModelResolver["model-provider-resolver<br/>Watches ExternalModel CRDs<br/>Resolves model → provider"]
            APITranslation["api-translation<br/>OpenAI ↔ Provider format<br/>(Anthropic, Azure, Bedrock, Vertex)"]
            APIKeyInjection["apikey-injection<br/>Watches labeled Secrets<br/>Injects auth headers"]
            NemoReqGuard["nemo-request-guard<br/>(optional)<br/>Input content rails"]
            NemoRespGuard["nemo-response-guard<br/>(optional)<br/>Output content rails"]

            ModelExtractor --> ModelResolver
            ModelResolver --> APITranslation
            APITranslation --> APIKeyInjection
            APIKeyInjection -.-> NemoReqGuard
            NemoReqGuard -.-> NemoRespGuard
        end

        CycleState["CycleState<br/>(per-request shared memory)"]
        ModelStore["modelInfoStore<br/>(in-memory, RWMutex)"]
        SecretStore["secretStore<br/>(in-memory, RWMutex)"]

        ModelResolver -->|writes provider info| CycleState
        APITranslation -->|reads provider info| CycleState
        APIKeyInjection -->|reads credential ref| CycleState

        ModelResolver -->|reads| ModelStore
        APIKeyInjection -->|reads| SecretStore
    end

    %% CRDs
    ExternalModelCR["ExternalModel CR<br/>inference.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1"]
    ExternalProviderCR["ExternalProvider CR<br/>inference.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1"]
    SecretCR["Secret<br/>(labeled bbr-managed=true)"]

    ExternalModelCR -->|reconciled into| ModelStore
    ExternalProviderCR -.->|referenced by| ExternalModelCR
    SecretCR -->|reconciled into| SecretStore

    %% Gateway API / Envoy
    Client["Client"]
    Gateway["Gateway API Gateway<br/>(Envoy Proxy)"]
    EnvoyFilter["Istio EnvoyFilter<br/>Attaches ExtProc"]

    Client -->|HTTPS/443| Gateway
    Gateway -->|gRPC ExtProc/9004| ExtProc
    EnvoyFilter -->|configures| Gateway
    ExtProc -->|mutated request| Gateway

    %% External Providers
    Gateway -->|HTTPS/443| OpenAI["OpenAI API"]
    Gateway -->|HTTPS/443| Anthropic["Anthropic API"]
    Gateway -->|HTTPS/443| Azure["Azure OpenAI API"]
    Gateway -->|HTTPS/443| Bedrock["AWS Bedrock API"]
    Gateway -->|HTTPS/443| Vertex["Google Vertex AI API"]

    %% NeMo
    NemoReqGuard -->|HTTP POST| NemoSvc["NeMo Guardrails Service<br/>/v1/guardrail/checks"]
    NemoRespGuard -->|HTTP POST| NemoSvc

    %% K8s API
    ModelResolver -->|Watch/List| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server<br/>HTTPS/443"]
    APIKeyInjection -->|Watch/List| K8sAPI

